#12201
The Eastern Plains, at the gate to New Hope~
You are in the Eastern Plains, which occupy the eastern side of the continent.
It is mainly open fields, whith the exception of some small trees, terribly
worn from the weather.  Seems not much can survive outside of the sanctuary
of the walls of town, at least not very well.  And with the openess of these
plains comes easy moveability.  All directions are open to you, supposing
you can keep from becoming lost.
Before you stands an enormous gate leading to the town of New Hope.
~
