The Eastern Plains~
You look to your side at the usual western stone wall.  It stands tall
at what you'd estimate a good twenty feet at least, all composed of large,
gray stones.  You look at it for a moment.  It is built well to keep anyone
from ever getting over it.  Though on closer examination of the wall you find
