The Eastern Plains~
You find the plains rather boring, and so you get down on your hands
and knees to count the blades of grass..............................
Yeppers, just as you thought!  There are two billion, ninety five million,
two hundred seven thousand, three hundred ninety eight blades of grass
here, which is five million, 3 thousand, nine hundred sixty one less
than the last area, and four million, three hundred thirty one thousand,
nine hundred ten more than the one before that.
~
